data.value: UPDATE [Stock] SET [FID] = @FID, [Fuel_Type] = @Fuel_Type, [Stock_Leters] = @Stock_Leters WHERE (([FID] = @Original_FID) AND ([Fuel_Type] = @Original_Fuel_Type) AND ([Stock_Leters] = @Original_Stock_Leters)); SELECT FID, Fuel_Type, Stock_Leters FROM Stock WHERE (FID = @FID)
